### ========================================
### POSTS API
### ========================================

### Create a new post (user123)
POST http://localhost:3001/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first post",
  "sender": "user123"
}

###
### Create another post (user456)
POST http://localhost:3001/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Second Post",
  "content": "This is another post with different content",
  "sender": "user456"
}

###
### Create a third post (user123 again)
POST http://localhost:3001/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Third Post by user123",
  "content": "Another post from the same user",
  "sender": "user123"
}

###
### GET all posts
GET http://localhost:3001/post

###
### GET post by ID (replace <post_id> with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3001/post/<post_id>

###
### GET posts by sender
GET http://localhost:3001/post?sender=user123

###
### GET posts by another sender
GET http://localhost:3001/post?sender=user456

###
### UPDATE a post (replace <post_id> with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:3001/post/<post_id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "content": "This content has been updated!",
  "sender": "user123"
}

###
### Test incomplete post (should return 400 error)
POST http://localhost:3001/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Incomplete Post"
}

### ========================================
### COMMENTS API
### ========================================

###
### Create a comment on a post (replace <post_id> with actual post ID)
POST http://localhost:3001/comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is a great post!",
  "sender": "commenter1",
  "postId": "<post_id>"
}

###
### Create another comment on the same post
POST http://localhost:3001/comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "I totally agree with this!",
  "sender": "commenter2",
  "postId": "<post_id>"
}

###
### Create a third comment from same user
POST http://localhost:3001/comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Adding more thoughts here",
  "sender": "commenter1",
  "postId": "<post_id>"
}

###
### GET all comments
GET http://localhost:3001/comment

###
### GET comment by ID (replace <comment_id> with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3001/comment/<comment_id>

###
### GET all comments for a specific post
GET http://localhost:3001/comment?postId=<post_id>

###
### UPDATE a comment (replace <comment_id> with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:3001/comment/<comment_id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "I changed my mind about this!",
  "sender": "commenter1"
}

###
### DELETE a comment (replace <comment_id> with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/comment/<comment_id>
